data.description: WELCOME HOME to this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home situated on approx. 0.82 of an acre. As you enter the front door, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room with open-concept to the dining room & kitchen. The kitchen offers ample counter space & cabinets followed by a very large laundry room. The extra large owner's suite is located off the main living room with enough space for an in-home office or nursery & has a luxurious garden tub with separate shower. This split-floorplan home also offers a large, 2nd living room with a fireplace, 3 guest bedrooms & 1 guest bath. ***NO SUBJECT TO OFFERS & NO SELLER FINANCING.
